From: Adham Faris <afaris@nvidia.com>
Date: Thu, 12 Oct 2023 12:27:45 -0700
Subject: net/mlx5e: Refactor rx_res_init() and rx_res_free() APIs
Patch-mainline: v6.7-rc1
Git-commit: d90ea84375b86051e3e648dc9a8fc99919da6b42
References: jsc#PED-3311

